      <title>中国支出下滑正压垮全球汽车制造商利润</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/bmw-earnings-drop-on-waning-demand-in-key-china-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[宝马汽车公司和大众汽车公司结束了全球汽车制造商痛苦的盈利期，因为它们正面临着电动汽车销量下滑和中国需求疲软的困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/bmw-earnings-drop-on-waning-demand-in-key-china-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 05:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
